{"tid":1308311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"組成小隊將文宣加lennon wall二合為一增大曝光度","createTime":"2019-07-12T00:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T08:50:50.000Z","uid":44028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc77ae86ed204ef7a505503523bee34d0013fd8","tid":1308311,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:48:43.000Z","msg":"我想問可唔可以同一日組幾組人，事前集合左share情報同宣傳單張或物資，之後分組去人多既地區（主要為：銅鑼灣，金鐘，觀塘，旺角，元朗同埋光復地區）開lennon wall.點解要十個人係因為可以隨時照應。事先亦印好文宣既活動傳單，係邀請人去果陣10個人分2/3小組去距離牆5-10分鐘既地點派傳單。最重要係遊行/光服之前果日必定要係果一區派，務求令當區居民收到傳單或知道聽日會有活動。<br />\n<br />\n而家有兩個問題係我地開始對lennon wall成效感到質疑，另外宣傳力度又唔夠大同廣，出面啲人唔會太知未來有咩活動或者政府有咩新計謀/議程。"},{"pid":"6ec12f8d9a56b40dffbeaff14511d73bc7d5539b","tid":1308311,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:50:40.000Z","msg":"如果遭遇廢老團就可以去下一個區或者同一區第二個地點去黎過"},{"pid":"516d65c41c9b427404a4ea696169402854d0d40e","tid":1308311,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:51:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d0e0cdfbfa9c4d10dbdbc05dd9c5c7806cdf696","tid":1308311,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:51:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"077de404a96eecbf3ed70452f9557304a51fd5c9","tid":1308311,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:52:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"687c461ff9cb7f9ccfb6dee4bea308c09d0db20a","tid":1308311,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:53:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d5a64452954f3f88e7d489e5c9d5e58f784614a4","tid":1308311,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:53:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ff472680cb2b05bacbc2e8e7e348d28be68db3bd","tid":1308311,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e2c0b8e6cac4bbc3a0f3b5da82e5b2aa2e55c791","tid":1308311,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit